text: Aleksandr Aleksandrovich Kokorin (Russian: Алекса́ндр Алекса́ндрович Коко́рин; born 19 March 1991) is a Russian professional football player. He plays for ACF Fiorentina. He has previously played for the Russian national team. ==References== * * == Other websites == * Player page on the official Russian Premier League site * Player page on the official Dynamo Moscow site Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers
